window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Supervillains do not merely play hooky. </p> <p>True, coming back to school after a month spent fighting - and defeating - adult superheroes is a bit of a comedown for the Inscrutable Machine. When offered the chance to skip school in the most dramatic way possible, Penelope Akk can't resist. With the help of a giant spider and mysterious red goo, she builds a spaceship and flies to Jupiter. </p> <p>Mutant goats. Secret human colonies. A war between three alien races with humanity as the prize. Robot overlords and evil plots. </p> <p>Penny and her friends find all this and more on Jupiter's moons, but what they don't find are any heroes to save the day. Fortunately, they have an angry 11-year-old and a whole lot of mad science.... </p>"; 
